{
  "3128220": {
    "name": "Nerd Simulator",
    "steam_appid": 3128220,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/extras/b1aed6cb42cdfcebb8f9cdd2ed7930e1.avif?t=1772061870\" width=1232 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >四十岁，没存款，没计划，还有一个每周都等着收房租的妈妈。欢迎来到梅尔文的世界——一款成人模拟器，每一个任务都会比你眨眼还快地失控。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">关于本作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的目标很简单：赚到足够的钱，终于搬离妈妈的家。怎么做？完全取决于你……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/extras/59c2a086f3abaac686a968103ecd7c86.poster.avif?t=1772061870\" width=1170 height=950 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/extras/59c2a086f3abaac686a968103ecd7c86.webm?t=1772061870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >去赌场碰碰运气，把一切押在加密货币上，或者和一些可疑的人混在一起！但要记住，你也可能同样迅速地失去一切——而那时……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/extras/bfada1fe8424dc1d5b1038ba82fb3741.poster.avif?t=1772061870\" width=1170 height=570 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/extras/bfada1fe8424dc1d5b1038ba82fb3741.webm?t=1772061870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >老实工作？噩梦。但有时这是唯一的选择。割草坪、刷厕所，或者在垃圾分拣站工作——赚得慢，但诚实！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/extras/0fe91ea96bf699494e5be1d2f9aca2e9.poster.avif?t=1772061870\" width=1170 height=570 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/extras/0fe91ea96bf699494e5be1d2f9aca2e9.webm?t=1772061870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >房租不够？去脱衣舞俱乐部兼职跳舞。身无分文？挑战你妈打一架！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/extras/356ade8ae80f9dc269a87226f9e6aeaa.poster.avif?t=1772061870\" width=1170 height=570 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/extras/356ade8ae80f9dc269a87226f9e6aeaa.webm?t=1772061870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人生不只是工作。去健身，画画，或者和一条金鱼做朋友，好让自己不至于疯掉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/extras/16aa79657a84a6b83ba5049752848381.poster.avif?t=1772061870\" width=1170 height=570 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128220/extras/16aa79657a84a6b83ba5049752848381.webm?t=1772061870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个世界上，没有什么是正常的。对白充满黑色幽默，角色徘徊在荒诞的边缘，每一步你都会问自己：“WTF?!”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">游戏内容</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >疯狂的剧情，充满荒谬的选择和不可预测的后果</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的2D与3D任务组合、完全可互动的梅尔文房间，以及他的指挥中心——Doors XD电脑</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数十个荒诞的小游戏，灵感来自梅尔文最离谱的工作和兼职</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理梅尔文的需求：睡眠、饥饿和膀胱（注意，他有时会很挑剔！）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >房间自定义和塑造你混乱生活的进度系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充满黑色幽默的对话和一群怪诞、夸张的人物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日常活动帮助梅尔文（勉强）保持理智：健身、绘画、奇怪的爱好等等</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >疯狂融合了模拟、喜剧与痛苦成人生活的混合体验</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">将 <i>Nerd Simulator</i> 添加到愿望单，准备迎接史上最怪异的成人模拟！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 意大利语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 波兰语, 法语, 德语, 简体中文, 俄语, 土耳其语",
